<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to WCC</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: black;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 450px;
            margin: 40px auto;
        }
        p {
            font-size:19px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 40px;
            line-height: 60px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .title-message {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 17px;
            color: rgb(85, 85, 85);
            
        } 
        .link-name {
            color: rgb(5, 69, 153);
            text-decoration: underline;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .user-detail {
            background-color: rgb(223, 223, 223);
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }

        .user-detail p {
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .footer p {
            font-size: 15px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="title">Welcome to the WCC</p>
        <p class="title-message">Excited to have on board. Let's get you up and running fast.</p>
        <p>Now access all your service from anywhere and across any devices</p>

        <p>Here are your Login details:</p>

        <div class="user-detail">
            <p>Web Address: <span class="link-name">https://localhost:5173</span></p>
            <p>Name: <span><%= name %></span></p>
            <p>Email: <span class="link-name"><%= email %></span></p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p>Thank you for joining, we hope you happy time!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any doubts, don't hesitate we are there. Write to us on - <span class="link-name">{email here}</span></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>